overview: 110% Surfing Techniques Volume 3 will improve your overall surfing performance, from catching more waves through to taking your 'off the lips' to the next level. The video includes tips and advice for all levels of surfing. This instructional surfing video has fault analysis, tips, techniques, common errors and lots of information. There is a regular foot and goofy foot version to pick from. Each version is 69 minutes duration in 1080p HD.
title: 110% Surfing Techniques Vol. 3
